{"tid":998353,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[又靠12碼] 垃圾球員賤種朗 真正垃圾實力update 20190128","createTime":"2019-01-28T02:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T03:01:25.000Z","uid":54373,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b3bf5d05938f710523c58048be55ce5a78ce2274","tid":998353,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:06:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">條垃圾靠12碼先入到波,完場d news 仲要作到話全靠佢入波反勝 (無提係12碼)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> <br />\n<br />\n本週<br />\n賤種朗 - 1射1入 (靠12M)<br />\n美斯 - 7射1入<br />\n<br />\n#數據post目的係唔想班賤朗迷再呃人<br />\n#上述數據由今季第1場比賽開始計算<br />\n#上述數據根據 who scored + 7m 賽後數據 每場累積而來<br />\n<br />\n賤種朗<br />\n聯賽: 134射15入球 (5球靠12碼) (11.1%)<br />\n歐聯: 27射1入球 1紅牌 (3.7%)<br />\n意大利社區盾 6射1入 (16.6%)<br />\n意大利盃: n射0入 (190113vs 榜尾博洛尼亞, 官方沒有數據)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>已射167球 得個17個入球 合共10.1%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美斯<br />\n聯賽: 89射19入球 (1球靠12碼) (21.3%)<br />\n歐聯: 20射6入球 0紅牌 (30%)<br />\n西班牙盃: n射1入 (190118vs 中游利雲特, 官方沒有數據)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>已109射入26球 合共23.8%</strong>"},{"pid":"8d21a72060fb41e1eff6b5cacc4751e3a8a15c71","tid":998353,"uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:10:23.000Z","msg":"意甲射入榜<br />\n<br />\n1st 加利亞雷拉(森) 20場 入16球 (4球12m)<br />\n2nd 沙柏達(阿) 21場 入15球 (1球12m)<br />\n2nd 賤種朗(蛆) 21場 入15球 <span style=\"color: red;\">(5球12m)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">靠12m 都上唔到第一 垃x圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"0656545933c1fb68e520f070e96a6198539586b0","tid":998353,"uid":58811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:18:07.000Z","msg":"大賽球員黎<br />\n普通聯賽出三成功力is okay"},